          <title>Oakland A's play last game at Coliseum Thursday afternoon</title>
          <description><![CDATA[OAKLAND, Calif. (KRON) -- After 57 years of Major League Baseball, the Oakland A's will play their last game at the Oakland Coliseum on Thursday afternoon. They will take on the Texas Rangers at 12:37 p.m. The A's are headed to Sacramento next season, and they plan to eventually go to Las Vegas.]]></description>
